videos.description: Michigan's Jon Teske throws a strike to Ignas Brazdeikis who finishes a tough layup for an and-1.
videos.headline: Brazdeikis finishes through contact for and-1

videos.description: Eli Brooks lobs it high to Jon Teske who slams it home through contact for a nasty one-handed flush.
videos.headline: Teske rises for alley-oop slam

videos.description: Ayo Dosunmu hustles back on defense and stuffs Zavier Simpson off the glass.
videos.headline: Illinois' Dosunmu elevates for rejection off the glass

videos.description: Illinois' Ayo Dosunmu is showing off his bounce as he rejects Zavier Simson's layup attempt off the glass for the second time of the game.
videos.headline: Dosunmu blocks Simpson's layup off the glass for 2nd time

videos.description: Michigan's Zavier Simpson draws defenders and finds Jon Teske who absorbs contact and lays it in for an and-1.
videos.headline: Simpson's finds Teske for and-1 finish

videos.description: Charles Matthews slips past Illinois' defenders and throws down a nice two-handed slam.
videos.headline: Matthews gets up for two-handed flush
